Introduction

Resonar (Korean: 레소나) is a South Korean project girl group formed through the show “Miss Back”. They officially debuted on December 16, 2020 with the single “Tantara”. The group is made up of Raina, Soyul, and Nada who are former members of After School, Crayon Pop & Wassup.
